Package: avesperu
Title: Access To The List Of Birds Species Names Of Peru
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul Efren", "Santos Andrade", , 
    "paulefrens@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375"))
Description: This package provides access to the data in the species list included in the book "Birds of Peru" and the "List of the Birds of Peru" the most complete and authoritative field guides to Peru's diverse neotropical landscape. The package includes detailed species accounts.The data is organized for easy access and use in R.
